---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import DocsSidebar from "../../components/DocsSidebar.astro";
---
<Layout
	title="Docs · flipagent"
	description="flipagent helps your AI agent resell on eBay — sourcing, scoring, buying, listing, fulfillment. Try it in two minutes."
>
	<div class="cmw cmw-bordered">
		<div class="docs-shell">
			<DocsSidebar />
			<article class="docs-content">
				<h1>Hey, this is <span class="accent">flipagent</span></h1>
				<p class="lead">It's the API for AI agents that resell on eBay. Sourcing, scoring, buying, listing, fulfillment — one key covers the whole thing.</p>

				<p style="margin-top:24px;">Easiest way to feel it is to just try it. We'll ask flipagent one real question and watch the answer come back. Pick the path that fits.</p>

				<div class="features" style="margin:18px 0 8px;">
					<a class="feature" href="/docs/quickstart/#mcp">
						<div class="ic">If you use Claude Code</div>
						<h3>Take the MCP path</h3>
						<p>One snippet in your config, one chat message, done.</p>
						<div style="margin-top:14px; color:var(--brand); font-size:13.5px;">Go →</div>
					</a>
					<a class="feature" href="/docs/quickstart/#playground">
						<div class="ic">If you don't</div>
						<h3>Use the playground</h3>
						<p>Open it in your browser, click run. Nothing to install.</p>
						<div style="margin-top:14px; color:var(--brand); font-size:13.5px;">Go →</div>
					</a>
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
